h=fb662922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBAj6Qv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBAj6Qv.gif&h=8056e3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOJO3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOJO3Q.gif&h=92e11c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOtUVJR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOtUVJR.gif&h=eaa393bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLA4yvw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLA4yvw.gif&h=3a86806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFOqhXb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFOqhXb.gif&h=b24b8c4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再提 捐款民調<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎分享"},{"pid":"cf227b114861cd4492097b984622bddc4f124bc1","tid":1303790,"uid":274858,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"見到中共做嘅嘢好似肆無忌憚 用盡一切方法侵略呢片土地 但正正係因為咁 我哋更加要用盡最後一口氣守護我哋嘅屋企"},{"pid":"6f24323656a73fe291c2074b102f178a1b6a05f3","tid":1303790,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1405000/1405900/result_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1405000%2F1405900%2Fresult_1024.jpg&h=bf7cfd9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c9803c7b1d275697161b663841ba3b89c1c54a6","tid":1303790,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"又想呃人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93906b1a6ccc0fbffc42d3f60b933c10dff34c21","tid":1303790,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cd442fe6638edf4544ab94d84177e964b08811","tid":1303790,"uid":211317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"對西方社會嚟講當然可以輕易放棄我地,但我地係香港人呀。我地既根就係呢到,我地可以做既真係盡力做自己可以做既野,然後期待奇跡。"},{"pid":"4ab1333508f077321c2a78d83474efd1310ef8a3","tid":1303790,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"整個簡單版畀廢老睇"},{"pid":"c83719952f617d89692dcdb8b02f14dcb5a82399","tid":1303790,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab1333508f077321c2a78d83474efd1310ef8a3","tid":1303790,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"整個簡單版畀廢老睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"廢老：跟中國有咩唔好？而家中國幾先進幾強大"},{"pid":"8ba5e19f0f02a10a8c825b277e42d80137187b26","tid":1303790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83719952f617d89692dcdb8b02f14dcb5a82399","tid":1303790,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab1333508f077321c2a78d83474efd1310ef8a3","tid":1303790,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"整個簡單版畀廢老睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"廢老：跟中國有咩唔好？而家中國幾先進幾強大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d424c664469559622b831b9e47af3891d910ac","tid":1303790,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"人哋唔救咪自己救囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854e3cd43987c3c7c3528813e0c886acd7e4a8b2","tid":1303790,"uid":184679,"like":0,"d